## Limitations

The findings are based on available online resources and may not encompass all aspects of how anxiety affects family and friends. The information is also limited to the perspectives shared in the articles and may not reflect the full diversity of experiences. Additionally, the lack of recent data in some sources may affect the current relevance of the findings. Further research, including interviews with mental health professionals and individuals affected by anxiety, could provide a more comprehensive understanding.